online\/2013\/12\/27\/providence-sabr-maa-usri-yusra\/","url_meta":{"origin":40165,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Victory comes with patience, hardship with ease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cKnow that there is much good in being patient with what you detest, victory will come with patience, relief will come with affliction, and 'with the hardship will come an ease.'\u201d (94:5) Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2803\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/hardship-debt-shade-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40165,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Helping others in the shade of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Yasar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would love to be shaded in the shade of Allah, let him help someone in hardship or waive a loan.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad\u00a015520 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,